_:N9bc3e429178441789d7001504a3fb161 <http://schema.org/description> "The National Housing Bank, a Homes England company, delivers purpose-led finance for housing delivery. We aim to break down barriers to investment at scale and accelerate the delivery and regeneration of places. NHB works with Homes England ." .
